title: The Vegan House
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Thai, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out
description: Hollywood vegan restaurant with extensive menu featuring various faux meat Thai food dishes, soups, curries, veggie sushi, pancakes, rice and noodles bowls, shabu shabu hot pot, and more. Small space, simple setup. Has 2 tables outside for seating. Parking on street. Different owners from Vegan House on Sunset Blvd in Silvelake.
